603
00:29:11,412 --> 00:29:12,652
What good news?

604
00:29:12,732 --> 00:29:13,732
My brother wrote a letter.

605
00:29:14,172 --> 00:29:14,692
He said

606
00:29:14,692 --> 00:29:16,212
