00:29:31,011 --> 00:29:32,051
That's not true.

619
00:29:32,492 --> 00:29:33,492
In my heart,

620
00:29:33,492 --> 00:29:34,611
besides your brother,

621
00:29:34,611 --> 00:29:35,732
