836
00:37:25,652 --> 00:37:26,612
Over the years,

837
00:37:26,612 --> 00:37:27,371
I've caught a few demons

838
00:37:27,572 --> 00:37:28,851
with our master

839
00:37:29,291 --> 00:37:31,291
